Built with [Next.js](https://nextjs.org/) and the [Bloque](https://github.com/user/bloques-reciclables) ecosystem.

## Getting Started

1. Install dependencies:

```bash
pnpm install
```

2. Copy the environment file and configure it:

```bash
cp .env.local.example .env.local
```

3. Start the development server:

```bash
pnpm dev
```

Open [http://localhost:3000](http://localhost:3000) in your browser.

## Stack

- **Next.js 14** - React framework with App Router
- **Tailwind CSS** - Utility-first CSS with @bloque/ui preset
- **@bloque/api-client** - API client for backend communication
- **@bloque/auth-react** - Authentication hooks and components
- **@bloque/types** - Shared TypeScript types
- **@bloque/ui** - UI components and design tokens
{% if include_multitenant %}
## Multi-Tenant

This project includes multi-tenant support via `TenantProvider` and `useTenant()`.
The tenant context is available in all authenticated routes.
{% endif %}

## Project Structure

```
src/
  app/
    layout.tsx        # Root layout with providers
    page.tsx          # Home page (redirect or login)
    login/
      page.tsx        # Login form
    dashboard/
      layout.tsx      # Dashboard layout with auth guard
      page.tsx        # Dashboard page
  lib/
    bloque-client.ts  # API client singleton
  providers/
    app-providers.tsx # Provider composition
  styles/
    globals.css       # Tailwind directives and CSS variables
```
